{"tid":2215936,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"浴血新城市︱商場由拒警到中門大開 和你唱抗爭成常態","createTime":"2020-09-24T10:22:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T10:38:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"13ca55f7ac42d516030b626e0d83829586b719db","tid":2215936,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:22:18.000Z","msg":"去年7月沙田發生「浴血新城市」事件，大批防暴警察闖入新城市廣場與示威者爆發激烈衝突，警方因亂闖商場惹批評，不少商場對警方「落閘」，一度拒絕警員亂闖，商場更成「和你Sing」、「和你Shop」場地，但其後商場迅速變臉，由拒警進場到中門大開，更有保安員因阻止警員入場被捕。有沙田區區議員指一年來部份商場對警察進場態度大變，有商場更向在場內唱歌的市民發警告信，卻無視警察肆意闖入執法，不但打壓和平示威，連市民人身自由亦受限制。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/MNTTCJNA2FGUNGT5AIADGINQ34/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FMNTTCJNA2FGUNGT5AIADGINQ34%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFMo9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=74709aa9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FMNTTCJNA2FGUNGT5AIADGINQ34%2F&h=50e9de1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/MNTTCJNA2FGUNGT5AIADGINQ34/</a>"},{"pid":"8457f0509790ceb02b410d71f8fe9b7751f12016","tid":2215936,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:22:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44aca686442ffa71d5c99c638939cb44d4be01d5","tid":2215936,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:24:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"666cf0d876b01d309615a6e2f9c8880663af3446","tid":2215936,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:29:20.000